stories.title: Century for Gilchrist as Australia take one-day series
stories.summary: With Adam Gilchrist hammering out a thunderous century, Australia shrugged aside South Africa's highest total in five matches to wrap up the Standard Bank one-day series by eight wickets at Kingsmead on Wednesday night
